<HEADLINE>
BOEING, MACHINISTS HUDDLE AS DEADLINE FOR FINAL OFFER NEARS 
</HEADLINE>
   (For use by New York Times News Service clients.)  
 By JAMES WALLACE  
 c.1999 Seattle Post-Intelligencer  
<TEXT>
<P>
   SEATTLE _ Weary negotiating teams from The Boeing Co. and its
