<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-08-28 10:25 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A2656 &Cx1f; taf-z
u s BC-FBC-SEASON-800(2TAKES     08-28 0766
