<P>
   KING-STAMP _ ATLANTA _ MLK postage stamp unveiled at 11 a.m. EDT
Saturday by Coretta Scott King at King Center. This is one of 15
stamps in a series honoring the most significant events of the
'60s, as voted on by postal customers. Others include Vietnam,
Packers winning championship, etc. Andrew Young will be master of
ceremonies. Campbell, Barnes and most of King family in attendance.
(Cook, Atlanta Journal-Constitution).
