   FOOTBALL/COLLEGES
</P>
<P>
   FBC-ARIZONA-PENNST _ Coverage of the college football opener
between Arizona and Penn State in the Pigskin Classic. (Barnhart,
Atlanta Journal-Constitution)
</P>
<P>
